QuestData.Title: More Heads Full of Ivory
QuestData.CompletionText: I still have a need for more pairs of ivory tusks from the wild elekk that roam this land. Unfortunately, my budget will no longer handle your cut of the profits. If you continue to provide me what I need, however, you will be ingratiating yourself with the Consortium.
QuestData.RewardText: Excellent, more fine tusk specimens, though some look a bit dingy.You have the far-reaching gratitude of the Consortium, $N.
